      "comment": "BAD KNEES (3) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Trunkey Mick (30.80) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Has ability and looks hard to stop. WITCHY WOMAN (1) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (30.35) at this track in a Grade 5. Expected to do much better this time. BURGLAR TOM (2) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (30.73) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can find the frame this time. SENTOSA (7) can sneak into the finish.",
